{"tid":798193,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成個人生起碼有一半到係返工你問我未必識答","createTime":"2018-08-29T06:15:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T06:49:28.000Z","uid":204797,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"69c591dbfc346398bd7a14f89155a470b59e26f9","tid":798193,"uid":204797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T06:15:17.000Z","msg":"返手然完半個人生<br />\n係香港退休資金至唔手然夠用<br />\n<br />\n講真有錢既人係香港只不過係渡下假<br />\n係香港根本就係窮人服侍貴人<br />\n<br />\n成半世係公司，賺極到係公司<br />\n完全唔手然明<br />\n點解有人打工打手然到好似自己公司<br />\n公司賺錢多手然過你幫公司慳既資源<br />\n<br />\n係香港官商勾結得真係好手然嚴重<br />\n一係識人 一係父幹 一係你真係中左六合彩<br />\n唔係個個人到係輪手然住返工<br />\n<br />\n你以為返金融同地產好手然好<br />\n到只不過係抽水角色<br />\n係香港買樓既人到係賣手然返被啲香港人<br />\n香港其實一直到係賺緊香港人既血汗錢<br />\n交手然曬啲稅一直到從未見過真係正當用途<br />\n<br />\n如誤請講<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n純吹姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c709edc0cd30d1194f5b439bb67dceef88fa7fb","tid":798193,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T06:17:55.000Z","msg":"做盛行？"},{"pid":"5202ebf06dad92b7104783e4335a68ff9f913964","tid":798193,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T06:18:32.000Z","msg":"手然你老母"},{"pid":"dac9b3b28fdd53efee5caf979d33f630eae0823d","tid":798193,"uid":204797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c709edc0cd30d1194f5b439bb67dceef88fa7fb","tid":798193,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T06:17:55.000Z","msg":"做盛行？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T06:19:19.000Z","msg":"做咕哩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd55a30882f4b1328e8b359597408773108b1e1e","tid":798193,"uid":204797,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5202ebf06dad92b7104783e4335a68ff9f913964","tid":798193,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T06:18:32.000Z","msg":"手然你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T0